  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;evocation&nbsp;[fire];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;druid 3, hunter 3, sorcerer/wizard 3;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a drop of sweat)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Effect</strong>&nbsp;ray<br>\n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Fortitude partial, see text;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>A wavering red ray projects from your finger. You must succeed on a ranged touch attack with the ray to hit your target.</p><p>The ray inflicts 1d4 points of nonlethal damage, causing the target to suffer from heatstroke as its body temperature dramatically increases. Except as noted above, this spell otherwise functions as <i>ray of exhaustion</i>.</p><p>Characters wearing heavy clothing or armor of any sort take a -4 penalty on their saves.</p>\n</div>\n",
